{"Id":560376,"Title":"近田诗十章","Dynasty":"明","Author":"孙承恩","Context":"有田有田，不远以阻。东郊西畴，厥壤膴膴。我黍我稷，我稼我穑。昏余作力，匪朝伊夕。中田有庐，有室有轩。桑麻当门，榆柳荫园。鸡鸣于陌，豚散于野。牛辞其軏，亦在墙下。言馌于亩，率我仆夫。时往时还，朝不及晡。涤之翼翼，箯之握握。载稛载积，堆户填阈。庖羞佐酒，烝尝妥侑。惟此伏臈，洽我亲友。于焉怡怡，于焉媞媞。率我故常，祖先之贻。思夫人生有涯，而谋则赊。厌厥隘卑，乃驰心荒遐。思夫人每忽易，而务厥难。曷忘乎近安，而冒彼远患。悠悠我怀，喟焉永叹。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"","Status":1,"Rank":0,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"1a0e7693c05704ca9b6e9a3e9a897252","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":6670442,"Sentence":"有田有田，不远以阻。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"yǒu tián yǒu tián ，bú yuǎn yi zǔ ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":0,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6670443,"Sentence":"东郊西畴，厥壤膴膴。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"dōng jiāo xī chóu ，jué rǎng hū hū ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":1,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6670444,"Sentence":"我黍我稷，我稼我穑。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"wǒ shǔ wǒ jì ，wǒ jià wǒ sè ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":2,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6670445,"Sentence":"昏余作力，匪朝伊夕。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"hūn yú zuō lì ，fěi cháo yī xī ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":3,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6670446,"Sentence":"中田有庐，有室有轩。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"zhōng tián yǒu lú ，yǒu shì yǒu xuān ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":4,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6670447,"Sentence":"桑麻当门，榆柳荫园。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"sāng mā dāng mén ，yú liu yīn yuán ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":5,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6670448,"Sentence":"鸡鸣于陌，豚散于野。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"jī mǐng yú mò ，tún sǎn yú yě ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":6,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6670449,"Sentence":"牛辞其軏，亦在墙下。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"nǐu cǐ jī yuè ，yì zài qiáng xià ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":7,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6670450,"Sentence":"言馌于亩，率我仆夫。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"yán yè yú mǔ ，lǜ wǒ pū fū ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort"